order of deployment:
1. saltstack master -- will be used to automate everything else
2. wireguard
3. docker swarm
4. traefik

## deployment steps:

salt master init:
wget https://repo.saltproject.io/bootstrap/stable/bootstrap-salt.sh && chmod +x bootstrap-salt.sh && sudo ./bootstrap-salt.sh -M stable 3007.1


salt minion command:
wget https://repo.saltproject.io/bootstrap/stable/bootstrap-salt.sh && chmod +x bootstrap-salt.sh && sudo ./bootstrap-salt.sh -P stable 3007.1

- apply top.sls


next up:
use salt pillar to join swarm from worker node


useful docs: https://docs.saltproject.io/en/latest/topics/tutorials/walkthrough.html#tutorial-salt-walk-through


